=== 《蝙蝠侠：元年》和《未来的蝙蝠侠》 ===
2000年1月，斯科特·罗森伯格（{{lang|en|Scott Rosenberg}}）拒绝了为《蝙蝠侠：元年》编写剧本的机会<ref>{{cite news|author = Brian Linder|work = IGN|title = Rosenberg Won't Penn ''Batman 5''|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/03/09/rosenberg-wont-pen-batman-5|date = 2000-03-09|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105053517/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/03/09/rosenberg-wont-pen-batman-5|archivedate = 2012-11-05|deadurl = yes}}</ref>。2000年中期，{{link-en|保罗·迪尼|Paul Dini}}、[[尼尔·斯蒂芬森|尼尔·斯蒂芬森]]和{{link-en|鲍兹·亚金|Boaz Yakin}}均获聘为《未来的蝙蝠侠》编写剧本，其中还计划由亚金出任导演，电影将根据华纳兄弟公司同名电影动画系列片改编<ref name=Dana>{{cite news|author = Dana Harris|url = http://variety.com/2000/film/news/wb-sends-pi-guy-into-the-bat-cave-1117786714/|title = WB sends ''Pi'' guy into the Bat Cave|work = Variety|date = 2000-09-21|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081019042354/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117786714|archivedate = 2008-10-19|deadurl = no}}</ref>。然而，华纳兄弟几乎立即就决定放弃《未来的蝙蝠侠》改为支持《蝙蝠侠：元年》<ref name=ass/>。与此同时，华纳兄弟选择忽视乔·舒马赫所表达的意向，聘请[[达伦·阿伦诺夫斯基|达伦·阿伦诺夫斯基]]来担任《蝙蝠侠：元年》的编剧和导演<ref name=Jen/><ref name=Dana/>阿伦诺夫斯基曾与[[弗兰克·米勒|弗兰克·米勒]]在一个最终被放弃的项目中合作过，他请来米勒与自己共同创作新电影的剧本<ref>{{cite news|author = Brian Linder|work = IGN|title = The Bat-Men Speak|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/10/16/the-bat-men-speak|date = 2000-10-16|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105053523/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/10/16/the-bat-men-speak|archive-date = 2012-11-05|dead-url = no}}</ref>。他们打算重启《蝙蝠侠》系列，“算是‘有些’基于漫画小说吧，”阿伦诺夫斯基说：“把有关蝙蝠侠你所能想到的一切全部抛弃掉！一切！我们要彻底地重新开始。”<ref>{{cite news|author = Brian Linder|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/12/06/aronofsky-talks-batman-year-oneagain|title = Aronofsky Talks ''Batman: Year One''...Again|work = IGN|date = 2000-12-06|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081019042359/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117788894|archive-date = 2008-10-19|dead-url = no}}</ref>曾多次与阿伦诺夫斯基合作的{{link-en|马修·利巴提克|Matthew Libatique}}获得了[[摄影师|摄影师]]的职位<ref>{{cite news|author = Andrew O. Thompson|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/12/06/aronofsky-talks-batman-year-oneagain|title = Matthew Libatique|work = Variety|date = 2000-11-08|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081019042359/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117788894|archivedate = 2008-10-19|deadurl = no}}</ref>。导演还联系了[[克里斯蒂安·贝尔|克里斯蒂安·贝尔]]请他出演蝙蝠侠，无独有偶，贝尔之后将出演《蝙蝠侠诞生》<ref>{{cite news|author = Adam Smith|title = The Original ''American Psycho''|url = https://archive.org/details/iamamerica00smit|work = Empire|date = 2005-07|pages = 74-80, 82, 84, 87}}</ref>。华纳兄弟还在同时推进[[衍生作品|衍生作品]]《[[猫女_(电影)|猫女]]》<ref>{{cite news|author = Michael Fleming|url = http://variety.com/2001/film/news/wb-judd-purr-fect-as-cat-1117796285/|title = WB: Judd purr-fect as ''Cat''|work = Variety|date = 2001-04-02|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081019042404/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117796285|archivedate = 2008-10-19|deadurl = no}}</ref>。然而到了2002年6月，公司又决定放弃《蝙蝠侠：元年》，改为支持《蝙蝠侠对超人》<ref>{{cite news|author = Dana Harris|url = http://variety.com/2002/film/news/wb-fewer-pix-more-punch-1117869140/|title = WB: fewer pix, more punch|work = Variety|date = 2002-06-30|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081019042439/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117869140|archivedate = 2008-10-19|deadurl = no}}</ref>。

=== 《蝙蝠侠对超人》 ===
华纳兄弟放弃了[[J·J·艾布拉姆斯|J·J·艾布拉姆斯]]撰写的《超人飞越》（{{lang|en|Superman: Flyby}}）剧本，这个项目之前已经获得了拍摄许可<ref name=reboot>{{cite book|author = David Hughes|title = Comic Book Movies|isbn = 0-7535-0767-6|publisher = Virgin Books|pages = 21–2|year = 2003}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author = Mike White|title = ''Superman'': Grounded|work = Cashiers du Cinemart|accessdate = 2008-02-03|url = http://www.impossiblefunky.com/archives/issue_15/15_superman.asp?IshNum=15|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080216230219/http://www.impossiblefunky.com/archives/issue_15/15_superman.asp?IshNum=15|archivedate = 2008-02-16|deadurl = yes}}</ref>，但导演约瑟夫·麦克金提·尼彻（{{lang|en|McG}}）决定退出接拍《[[霹雳娇娃：全速进攻|霹雳娇娃：全速进攻]]》<ref name=Stallville>{{cite news|author = Daniel Fierman; Nancy Miller; Brian M. Raftery|title = Stallville?|work = Entertainment Weekly|url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,432553~1~0~itsburdenitspain--its,00.html|date = 2003-03-14|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130624132744/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C432553~1~0~itsburdenitspain--its%2C00.html|archivedate = 2013-06-24|deadurl = yes}}</ref>，公司于是联系[[沃尔夫冈·彼德森|沃尔夫冈·彼德森]]来执导<ref name=Dynamic>{{cite news|author = Brian M. Raftery; Nancy Miller|title = Dynamic Duel|work = Entertainment Weekly|url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,321972~1~0~holyfranchiseinsidebatman,00.html|date = 2002-07-09|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080106114014/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C321972~1~0~holyfranchiseinsidebatman%2C00.html|archivedate = 2008-01-06|deadurl = no}}</ref>。可到了2001年8月<ref>{{cite news|author = Brian Linder|title = More ''Batman'', ''Superman'' Insanity at WB|work = IGN|date = 2001-08-09|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/08/09/more-batman-superman-insanity-at-wb|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131030213652/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/08/09/more-batman-superman-insanity-at-wb|archive-date = 2013-10-30|dead-url = no}}</ref>，安德鲁·凯文·沃克（{{lang|en|Andrew Kevin Walker}}）向华纳兄弟公司提出了《蝙蝠侠对超人》的构思，于是公司又一次改变了主意，他们暂时搁置了艾布拉姆斯的剧本，不过彼德森仍然担任导演<ref name=Dynamic/>。之后公司还请来阿齐瓦·高斯曼对沃克的剧本进行改写<ref name=ass/>。

高斯曼改写的剧本于2002年6月21日完成，故事中已经从打击犯罪的生涯中退休5年的布鲁斯·韦恩正经历一场{{link-en|精神崩溃|Mental breakdown}}，[[阿尔弗莱德·潘尼沃斯|阿尔弗莱德·潘尼沃斯]]、[[詹姆斯·戈顿_(漫画)|詹姆斯·戈顿]]及迪克·格雷森均已故世，不过当他遇上美丽的伊丽莎白·米勒时一切问题似乎都迎刃而解了。与此同时，[[超人|克拉克·肯特]]前不久刚与深爱的路易斯·莱恩离婚而郁郁寡欢，他与布鲁斯成了好友，并且还是对方与伊丽莎白·米勒成婚时的伴郎。然而两人度蜜月时，伊丽莎白被小丑所杀，布鲁斯因此不得不再次穿上蝙蝠侠战衣并决心报仇，但超人不希望他意气用事于是加以劝阻。伤心而愤怒的布鲁斯发现这一事件还牵涉到[[雷克斯·路瑟|雷克斯·路瑟]]于是寻求超人的帮助。但克拉克又与另一位女子陷入了情网，因此拒绝了布鲁斯的请求。布鲁斯为此将伊丽莎白的惨死怪责在克拉克身上，两人变得敌对起来。不过当蝙蝠侠和超人发现这一切原来正是路瑟的一个大阴谋时，他们决定联合起来阻止他<ref>{{cite news|author = Akiva Goldsman|title = ''Batman vs Superman'' 2nd Draft|work = Daily Scripts|url = http://www.dailyscript.com/scripts/asylum.pdf|date = 2002-06-21|accessdate = 2013-05-25|format = PDF|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070928014936/http://www.dailyscript.com/scripts/asylum.pdf|archivedate = 2007-09-28|deadurl = no}}</ref>。

克里斯蒂安·贝尔和[[乔什·哈奈特|乔什·哈奈特]]分别拒绝了出演蝙蝠侠和超人的邀请<ref name=Stallville/><ref>{{cite news|author = Stax|title = ''Batman vs. Superman'' Shelved!|work = IGN|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/08/13/batman-vs-superman-shelved|date = 2002-08-13|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080210032811/http://movies.ign.com/articles/367/367576p1.html|archivedate = 2008-02-10|deadurl = no}}</ref>，原计划在2003年初开始电影的主体拍摄工作，拍摄周期约为5至6个月，发行日期预计为2004年中期<ref>{{cite news|author = Brian Linder|title = ''Batman vs. Superman'' in '04|work = [[IGN|IGN]]|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/07/09/batman-vs-superman-in-04|date = 2002-07-09|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131030215319/http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/07/09/batman-vs-superman-in-04|archive-date = 2013-10-30|dead-url = no}}</ref>。可是在华纳兄弟已经为《蝙蝠侠对超人》给出拍摄许可一个月后，导演彼得森选择接拍《[[特洛伊_(电影)|特洛伊]]》而退出<ref name=ass/>，于是公司决定暂时搁置拍摄，转而开发一个新的《蝙蝠侠》重启系列<ref name=ass/>。彼得森之后还是表示有兴趣执导《蝙蝠侠对超人》<ref>{{cite news|author=A.C. Ferrante|title=Profile: Wolfgang Peterson Reinvents ''Troy'' for DVD With New Director's Cut|publisher=If Magazine|date=2007-09-18|url=http://ifmagazine.com/feature.asp?article=2370|accessdate=2013-05-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071212141607/http://ifmagazine.com/feature.asp?article=2370|archivedate=2007-12-12|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，布莱恩·辛格也有同样的想法<ref>{{cite news|author=Clint Morris|title=Singer considering ''Batman Vs.Superman''?|publisher=Moviehole|date=2006-07-07|url=http://www.moviehole.net/news/20060707_singer_considering_batman_vssu.html|accessdate=2013-05-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080203231049/http://www.moviehole.net/news/20060707_singer_considering_batman_vssu.html|archivedate=2008-02-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。在2007年电影《[[我是传奇|我是传奇]]》的片头，[[時報廣場|时代广场]]上有一条巨大的横幅上面显示着超人和蝙蝠侠的标志。这正是撰写了《蝙蝠侠对超人》和《我是传奇》剧本的阿齐瓦·高斯曼在片中所开的玩笑<ref>{{cite news|author=Larry Carroll|title='Batman Vs. Superman' Coming In 2009, But Will We Live To See It?|publisher=MTV Movies Blog|date=2007-12-03|url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/12/03/batman-vs-superman-coming-in-2009-but-will-we-live-to-see-it/|accessdate=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029210312/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/12/03/batman-vs-superman-coming-in-2009-but-will-we-live-to-see-it/|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2013-06-25 |title=Batman vs Superman Poster From I Am Legend |url=http://themovieblog.com/2007/batman-vs-superman-poster-from-i-am-legend/ |archivedate=2013-04-21 |date=2007-12-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421002429/http://themovieblog.com/2007/batman-vs-superman-poster-from-i-am-legend/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

