=== 《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》（2005年） ===
{{main|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻}}
导演兼[[编剧|编剧]][[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]和另一位编剧[[大卫·S·高耶|大卫·S·高耶]]于2003年初开始为《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》出力<ref name=capture>{{cite news|author = Michael Flemming|url = http://variety.com/2003/film/news/batman-captures-director-nolan-1117879566/|title = ''Batman'' captures director Nolan|work = Variety|date = 2003-01-27|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081019042501/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117879566|archivedate = 2008-10-19|deadurl = no}}</ref>，旨在建立一个更黑暗、更逼真的基调，人性和现实主义将成为电影的基础<ref name="beautiful">{{cite news|author = Marc Graser; Cathy Dunkley|url = http://variety.com/2004/biz/news/the-bat-and-the-beautiful-1117899714/|title = The bat and the beautiful|work = Variety|date = 2004-02-08|accessdate = 2013-06-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150726041347/http://variety.com/2004/biz/news/the-bat-and-the-beautiful-1117899714/|archive-date = 2015-07-26|dead-url = no}}</ref>。电影的拍摄工作主要是在[[英国|英国]]和[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]进行的<ref>{{cite news|title=''Batman Begin'' goes to the source|work=The Kansas City Star|date=2004-06-25}}</ref><ref name=EMP>{{cite web|url=http://www.emporis.com/building/35eastwackerdrive-chicago-il-usa|accessdate=2013-06-25|year=2007|title=35 East Wacker Drive|publisher=Emporis|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102100702/http://www.emporis.com/building/35eastwackerdrive-chicago-il-usa|archive-date=2014-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>，电影的中特技镜头主要使用的是传统的特技手段和[[比例模型|比例模型]]，尽可能少用[[电脑绘图|电脑绘图]]来达成。[[克里斯汀·貝爾|克里斯汀·貝爾]]扮演蝙蝠侠，[[连姆·尼森|连姆·尼森]]饰演忍者大师（一度伪装成亨利·杜卡德），[[席尼·墨菲|席尼·墨菲]]出演[[稻草人_(漫画)|稻草人]]，[[凯蒂·霍姆斯|凯蒂·霍姆斯]]诠释蝙蝠侠青梅竹马的邻家女孩[[瑞秋·道斯|瑞秋·道斯]]。此外，电影还特别制作了一辆新的[[蝙蝠车|蝙蝠车]]和蝙蝠衣<ref name="batmobile">{{cite web|first=Marshall|last=Brain|url=http://entertainment.howstuffworks.com/arts/comic-books/batmobile.htm|title=How the Batmobile Works|work=HowStuffWorks|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130625125343/http://entertainment.howstuffworks.com/arts/comic-books/batmobile.htm|archive-date=2013-06-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="batsuit">{{cite web |url=http://www2.warnerbros.com/batmanbegins/productionnotes/# |title=''Batman Begins'' Production Notes – The Batsuit & Gadgetry |publisher=Warner Bros. |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061028060305/http://www.cinemareview.com/production.asp?prodid=3003 |archive-date=2006-10-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》于2005年6月15日上映，获得了商业和评论上的双丰收。在美国和加拿大的3858家电影院首周入账即达4800万美元，全球总票房3.74亿美元，[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上的“新鲜度”为85%。评论家指出恐惧是一个贯穿电影始终的主题，并表示与以往的电影相比，《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》的基调也更加阴暗。影片获得了[[第78届奥斯卡金像奖|第78届奥斯卡金像奖]][[学院奖最佳摄影奖|摄影奖]]提名，另外还有3项[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]提名<ref name=imdbawards>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0372784/awards|title=Batman Begins (2005) – Awards|publisher=IMDb|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130311023739/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0372784/awards|archive-date=2013-03-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在《[[帝国_(杂志)|帝国]]》杂志上评选的史上500部最佳电影中名列第81位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/500/83.asp|title=Empire's 500 Greatest Movies of All Time|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026035337/http://www.empireonline.com/500/83.asp|archive-date=2012-10-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>，截止2013年6月仍然保持在[[互联网电影数据库|互联网电影数据库]]上的“Top 250”中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0372784/|title=Batman Begins (2005)|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130625033711/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0372784/|archive-date=2013-06-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士》（2008年） ===
{{Main|蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士}}
[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]继续出任导演，并请来他的弟弟[[乔纳森·诺兰|強納森]]一起编写续集的剧本，[[克里斯汀·貝爾|克里斯汀·貝爾]]也回归《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士》继续扮演蝙蝠侠。[[希斯·莱杰|希斯·莱杰]]和[[艾伦·艾克哈特|艾伦·艾克哈特]]加盟分别饰演[[小丑_(角色)|小丑]]和[[双面人|双面人]]哈维·丹特。电影的主体拍摄工作于2007年4月至11月在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]进行，其它拍摄地点包括[[英国|英国]]和[[香港|香港]]。2008年1月22日，已经参加完电影拍摄的希斯·莱杰因处方药品事故不幸逝世，年仅28岁。华纳兄弟公司原本为《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士》展开了[[病毒营销|病毒营销]]，开发了宣传网站和预告片，还使用了莱杰扮演小丑的醒目照片。不过莱杰去世后，公司也重新调整了宣传手段<ref>{{Cite news|author=Marshall Crook; Peter Sanders|title=Advertising: Will Marketing Change After Star's Death?|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB120113527501911813.html|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2008-01-24|accessdate=2013-06-25|pages=B1|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080504052613/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB120113527501911813.html|archivedate=2008-05-04|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2008/SHOWBIZ/Movies/01/24/ledger.films/index.html?iref=mpstoryview|title=Ledger's Death Puts Last Films in a Bind|publisher=CNN|date=2008-01-24|accessdate=2013-06-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080726062210/http://www.cnn.com/2008/SHOWBIZ/Movies/01/24/ledger.films/index.html?iref=mpstoryview|archivedate=2008-07-26|deadurl=no}}</ref>。电影获得了很好的评价<ref name="Paste">{{cite web|title=The 50 Best Movies of the Decade (2000–2009)|url=http://www.pastemagazine.com/blogs/lists/2009/11/50-best-movies-of-the-decade-2000-2009.html?p=4|work=Paste Magazine|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2009-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130830063057/http://www.pastemagazine.com/blogs/lists/2009/11/50-best-movies-of-the-decade-2000-2009.html?p=4|archive-date=2013-08-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Metadecade">{{cite web|title=Film Critics Pick the Best Movies of the Decade|url=http://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-pick-the-best-movies-of-the-decade|work=Metacritic|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2010-01-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6pBuFqa6Q?url=http://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-pick-the-best-movies-of-the-decade|archive-date=2017-03-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Empiredecade">{{cite web|title=Review of the Decade – Year-By-Year: Empire's Films Of The Decade|url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/reviewofthedecade/films-of-the-decade/9.asp|work=Empire Magazine|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121116175210/http://www.empireonline.com/features/reviewofthedecade/films-of-the-decade/9.asp|archive-date=2012-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并且创下了多项票房方面的纪录<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/records/ |title=Movie Records |publisher=the-numbers.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508235827/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/records/ |archivedate=2013-05-08 |accessdate=2013-05-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，全球电影票房收入更突破10亿美元，並成為首部全球票房逾10億美元的蝙蝠俠電影和[[2008年電影#_最高票房|2008年全球票房最高的電影]]，以及克里斯多福·諾蘭首部全球票房逾10億美元的電影；此外影片还在[[第81届奥斯卡金像奖|第81届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中获得了8项提名，并最後拿下[[学院奖最佳音效剪辑奖|音效剪辑奖]]和[[学院奖最佳男配角奖|男配角奖]]（希斯·莱杰）<ref name="Oscars2009">{{Cite news|url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/81st-winners.html|title=The 81st Academy Awards (2009) Nominees and Winners|accessdate=2013-06-25|work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|publisher=AMPAS|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224033708/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/81st-winners.html|archive-date=2013-12-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 《黑暗騎士：黎明昇起》（2012年） ===
{{Main|黑暗騎士：黎明昇起}}
《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士崛起》是诺兰蝙蝠侠三部曲的收山之作<ref>{{cite news | author = Jeff Jensen | url = http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/11/30/christopher-nolan-batman-inception/ | title = Christopher Nolan on his 'last' Batman movie, an 'Inception' videogame, and that spinning top | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2010-11-30 | accessdate = 2013-06-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101202065701/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/11/30/christopher-nolan-batman-inception/ | archivedate = 2010-12-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，他希望这部电影的故事情节可以让他在情感上保持投入。“在一个更加表面化的层次上，我必须思考一个问题”，他说，“有哪些系列的第三部电影被认为是一部佳作？”<ref>{{cite news|first=Geoff|last=Boucher|title=Christopher Nolan on 'Dark Knight' and its box-office billion: 'It's mystifying to me'|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2008-10-27|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/christopher-nol/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130609230638/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/christopher-nol/|archivedate=2013-06-09|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2013-06-25}}. [https://www.webcitation.org/5xM0ssHEH?url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/2008/10/27/christopher-nol/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fherocomplex.latimes.com%2F2008%2F10%2F27%2Fchristopher-nol%2F WebCitation archive].</ref>他重新回到起点来寻找一个必要的方式继续这个故事，但担心会在拍摄中途时发现续集变得有些多余<ref>{{cite news|title=Nolan Talks DARK KNIGHT Blu-Ray, a 100,000 Person Screening of the Film (Featuring Live Q & A w/ Nolan), TDK Sequel, and More!!|author="Merrick" (pseudonym)|work=Ain't It Cool News|date=2008-12-05|url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/39348|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5xLwpPIh8?url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/39348|archivedate=2011-03-21|deadurl=yes|access-date=2013-06-25}}. .</ref>。2008年12月，诺兰初步完成了一个故事大纲，然后接拍了《[[盗梦空间|盗梦空间]]》<ref>{{cite news| first=Scott| last=Bowles| title=For now, Nolan and Batman will rest in 'Dark' glory| work=USA Today| date=2008-12-07| url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-12-07-dark-knight-nolan_N.htm?csp=34| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025113702/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-12-07-dark-knight-nolan_N.htm?csp=34| archivedate=2012-10-25| deadurl=yes| accessdate=2013-06-25}}. [https://www.webcitation.org/5xM0zLBMw?url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-12-07-dark-knight-nolan_N.htm?csp=34%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Flife%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2F2008-12-07-dark-knight-nolan_N.htm%3Fcsp%3D34 WebCitation archive].</ref>。2010年2月，大卫·S·高耶和乔纳森·诺兰开始创作剧本<ref>{{cite news|author = Finke, Nikki, and Mike Fleming|title = It's A Bird! It's A Plane! It's Chris Nolan! He'll Mentor Superman 3.0 And Prep 3rd Batman|publisher = Deadline.com|date = 2010-02-09|url = http://www.deadline.com/2010/02/its-a-bird-its-a-plane-its-chris-nolan-hell-mentor-superman-3-0-while-preparing-3rd-batman/|accessdate = 2013-06-25|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5xLwx0v1Q?url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/02/its-a-bird-its-a-plane-its-chris-nolan-hell-mentor-superman-3-0-while-preparing-3rd-batman/|archivedate = 2011-03-21}}. .</ref>。之后高耶离开去参加《[[超人：钢铁之躯|超人：钢铁之躯]]》的拍摄，而乔纳森则继续根据自己哥哥和高耶的构想进行编写<ref>{{cite news |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/03/christopher-nolan-takes-flight-with-superman-we-have-a-fantastic-story-1.html |title=Christopher Nolan takes flight with Superman: 'We have a fantastic story' [UPDATED] |last=Boucher |first=Geoff |date=2010-03-10 |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100704194608/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/03/christopher-nolan-takes-flight-with-superman-we-have-a-fantastic-story-1.html |archivedate=2010-07-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[汤姆·哈迪|汤姆·哈迪]]和[[安妮·海瑟薇|安妮·海瑟薇]]也加盟本片分别出演[[班恩_(漫画)|班恩]]和[[猫女|猫女]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Jensen |first=Jeff |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/01/19/batman-hathaway-catwoman-hardy-bane-dark-knight-rises/ |title='The Dark Knight Rises' scoop: Anne Hathaway, Tom Hardy join cast |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2011-01-19 |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130619160053/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/01/19/batman-hathaway-catwoman-hardy-bane-dark-knight-rises/ |archivedate=2013-06-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[喬瑟夫·高登-李維|喬瑟夫·高登-李維]]获选出演[[罗宾_(漫画)|约翰·布莱克]]<ref name=variety3-18>{{cite news |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |url=http://variety.com/2011/film/news/gordon-levitt-s-dark-knight-role-revealed-1118034129/ |title=Gordon-Levitt's 'Dark Knight' role revealed |work=Variety |date=2011-03-18 |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603041456/http://variety.com/2011/film/news/gordon-levitt-s-dark-knight-role-revealed-1118034129/ |archivedate=2013-06-03 |deadurl=yes }}. [https://www.webcitation.org/5xLwfOuHb?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118034129?refCatId=13%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.variety.com%2Farticle%2FVR1118034129%3FrefCatId%3D13 WebCitation.org]</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Jeff Labrecque|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/21/joseph-gordon-levitt-dark-knight-rises/|title=Joseph Gordon Levitt joins 'Dark Knight Rises'... but not as Falcone|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2011-03-21|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526050709/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/21/joseph-gordon-levitt-dark-knight-rises/|archive-date=2013-05-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此外加盟的还有[[玛丽昂·歌迪亚|玛丽昂·歌迪亚]]，电影于2011年5月开拍至11月结束<ref>{{cite news | first = Phil | last = de Semlyen | url = http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=29533 | title = Exclusive: The Dark Knight Rises In May | date = 2010-11-19 | work = Empire | accessdate = 2013-06-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130511200851/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=29533 | archivedate = 2013-05-11 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。诺兰选择不采用[[三维电影|3D]]技术来进行拍摄，不过使用了[[IMAX|IMAX]]格式来提高画面质量和规模，希望可以在保持电影与前两部风格一致的同时也可以推动技术的进步<ref name="release">{{cite news |url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/2010/10/27/nolan-dark-knight-rises-finds-the-future-in-imax-not-3d/ |title=Nolan: 'Dark Knight Rises' finds the future in IMAX, not 3-D |last=Boucher |first=Geoff |date=2010-10-27 |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101030034239/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/2010/10/27/nolan-dark-knight-rises-finds-the-future-in-imax-not-3d/ |archivedate=2010-10-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。诺兰与IMAX副总裁大卫·奈特利有过数次会面，商讨在数字IMAX影院放映的物流运输安排<ref name="ColliderIMAX">{{cite news|first = Steve|last = Weintraub|title = Exclusive: Exclusive: David Keighley (Head of Re-Mastering IMAX) Talks 'The Dark Knight', 'The Dark Knight Rises', 'Tron: Legacy', New Cameras, More|work = Collider|date = 2010-12-22|url = http://collider.com/david-keighley-imax-interview-the-dark-knight-rises-tron-legacy/66297|accessdate = 2013-06-25|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5xLyzQpYH?url=http://collider.com/david-keighley-imax-interview-the-dark-knight-rises-tron-legacy/66297|archivedate = 2011-03-21}}. .</ref>。《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士崛起》中使用IMAX拍摄的镜头数量要多于《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士》<ref name="ColliderIMAX"/>。[[摄影师|摄影师]][[瓦利·費思特|瓦利·費思特]]曾表示有意将整部电影都用IMAX拍摄<ref>{{cite news | author = Todd Gilchrist | url = http://blog.moviefone.com/2010/04/20/wally-pfister-talks-about-shooting-batman-3-in-3-d/ | title = Cinematographer Wally Pfister Talks About Shooting 'Batman 3' in 3-D | date = 2010-04-20 | work = Moviefone | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130530205015/http://blog.moviefone.com/2010/04/20/wally-pfister-talks-about-shooting-batman-3-in-3-d/ | archivedate = 2013-05-30 | accessdate = 2013-05-29 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://daily.bhaskar.com/article/ENT-gotham-city-crumbles-in-batman--the-dark-knight-rises-teaser-poster-2256595.html?HF-3=|title=Batman teaser poster: Gotham city topples as 'The Dark Knight Rises'|work=Daily Bhaskar|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714224840/http://daily.bhaskar.com/article/ENT-gotham-city-crumbles-in-batman--the-dark-knight-rises-teaser-poster-2256595.html?HF-3=|archive-date=2011-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士崛起》上映后获得了不錯的评价，并且票房上更胜前作，达到10.81亿美元，使其成為第二部全球票房逾10億美元的蝙蝠俠系列電影作品。

==三部曲後==
2011年3月，华纳兄弟公司总裁杰夫·罗宾诺夫（Jeff Robinov）表示下一部蝙蝠侠电影将会是一次重新创作，克里斯托弗·诺兰与[[艾玛·托马斯|艾玛·托马斯]]夫妇将共同担任[[制片人|制片人]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Ben Fritz | url = http://herocomplex.latimes.com/2011/03/29/justice-league-the-movie-warner-chief-sets-sights-on-team-up-film-and-reinventing-batman/ | title = Justice League, the movie? Warner chief sets sights on team-up film and ‘reinventing’ Batman | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2011-03-29 | accessdate = 2013-06-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130205000746/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/2011/03/29/justice-league-the-movie-warner-chief-sets-sights-on-team-up-film-and-reinventing-batman/ | archivedate = 2013-02-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。但是，两人决定从事其他项目。在接受《[[SFX_(杂志)|SFX]]》采访时托马斯表示，“三部曲的一个好处就是感觉你可以有始有终，就像是一部普通的电影可以拍得特别长。我实在看不出他（诺兰）还能保持兴趣另拍一部基本上只是盘旋在不同坏蛋之间的电影。”<ref>{{cite news | author = Matt Maytum | url = http://www.totalfilm.com/news/emma-thomas-says-christopher-nolan-will-never-make-another-batman-film | title = Emma Thomas says Christopher Nolan will never make another Batman film | work = Total Film | date = 2012-06-23 | accessdate = 2013-06-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120908203726/http://www.totalfilm.com/news/emma-thomas-says-christopher-nolan-will-never-make-another-batman-film | archivedate = 2012-09-08 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>有报道称下一次蝙蝠侠重现大银幕将是在[[正义联盟|正义联盟]]电影后，因此这个角色将引入正义联盟电影中，而不会再有单独作为主角的作品，并且还会成为[[DC漫画改编电影列表|DC电影宇宙]]的一部分<ref>{{cite news |url=http://batman-news.com/2012/08/28/batman-to-get-rebooted-in-2015-justice-league-movie/ |title=Batman to get rebooted in 2015 Justic League Movie |date=2012-08-28 |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120915061244/http://batman-news.com/2012/08/28/batman-to-get-rebooted-in-2015-justice-league-movie/ |archivedate=2012-09-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。但到了2013年3月，又有克里斯托弗·诺兰将负责拍摄所有与DC漫画宇宙有关角色电影的传闻浮出水面，称他将与《超人：钢铁之躯》的导演[[扎克·施奈德|扎克·施奈德]]一起制作一部正义联盟电影，其中施奈德还有考虑执导。报道中还称克里斯蒂安·贝尔将继续出演蝙蝠侠，而贝尔则表示如果有诺兰的参与，他愿意继续<ref>{{cite web|url=http://latino-review.com/2013/03/03/exclusive-dcu-takeover-huge-developments-justice-league/|title=EXCLUSIVE: The DCU Takeover & HUGE Developments on ‘Justice League’|author=El Mayimbe|publisher=Latino Review|date=2013-03-03|accessdate=2013-06-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130429122718/http://latino-review.com/2013/03/03/exclusive-dcu-takeover-huge-developments-justice-league/|archivedate=2013-04-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/03/04/report-bale-to-return-as-batman-in-justice-league|title=Report: Bale to Return as Batman in Justice League?|last=O'Brien|first=Lucy|date=2013-03-03|accessdate=2013-06-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603073203/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/03/04/report-bale-to-return-as-batman-in-justice-league|archivedate=2013-06-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/markhughes/2013/03/03/christopher-nolan-returns-to-batman-and-oversees-team-up-movie/|title=Christopher Nolan In Talks To Oversee Justice League, More Batman|last=Hughes|first=Mark|date=2013-03-03|accessdate=2013-06-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525133922/http://www.forbes.com/sites/markhughes/2013/03/03/christopher-nolan-returns-to-batman-and-oversees-team-up-movie/|archivedate=2013-05-25|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=34121|title=Dark Knight Rises: Is This The End?|last=O'Hara|first=Helen|date=2012-05-29|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130620051416/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=34121|archive-date=2013-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士崛起》的结尾，约瑟夫·高登-莱维特扮演的约翰·布莱克继承了蝙蝠洞，有观点认为这意识着将来可能会有[[衍生作品|衍生作品]]<ref name=MTV08102010 />。但高登-莱维特之后表示，《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士崛起》的确是诺兰蝙蝠侠系列电影的收山之作<ref name=MTV08102010>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1690664/dark-knight-rises-john-blake.jhtml |title='Dark Knight Rises': What's The Future Of John Blake? – Music, Celebrity, Artist News |publisher=MTV |date=2012-07-27 |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108111910/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1690664/dark-knight-rises-john-blake.jhtml |archivedate=2012-11-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。安妮·海瑟薇表示自己有意继续出演塞琳娜·凯尔一角，她也承认只要有诺兰的参与，她愿意单独接拍一部《猫女》电影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a394706/anne-hathaway-on-catwoman-spin-off-it-would-be-lovely-to-see-more.html |title=Anne Hathaway on Catwoman spin-off: 'It would be lovely to see more' |work=Digital Spy |date=2012-07-23 |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603144456/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a394706/anne-hathaway-on-catwoman-spin-off-it-would-be-lovely-to-see-more.html |archivedate=2013-06-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。
