movie... but that's not the big news|work=io9|date=2013-07-20|accessdate=2013-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722040226/http://io9.com/theyre-doing-a-superman-batman-movie-but-thats-not-851711013|archive-date=2013-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。高耶在2013年[[聖地亞哥國際動漫展|聖地亞哥國際動漫展]]超人75週年活動中表示，續集的片名有可能是《超人大戰蝙蝠俠》（Superman Vs Batman）或《蝙蝠俠大戰超人》（Batman Vs Superman）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/07/23/comic-con-man-of-steel-sequel-likely-called-batman-vs-superman|title=Comic-Con: Man of Steel Sequel Likely Called Batman Vs. Superman|last=Collura|first=Scott|date=2013-07-23|accessdate=2013-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140806165433/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/07/23/comic-con-man-of-steel-sequel-likely-called-batman-vs-superman|archive-date=2014-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這部電影於2014年在[[多倫多|多倫多]]開拍，而不是像《超人：鋼鐵英雄》是在溫哥華拍攝<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vancitybuzz.com/2013/07/man-of-steel-2-production-departs-vancouver-for-toronto/ |title=MAN OF STEEL 2 PRODUCTION DEPARTS VANCOUVER FOR TORONTO |access-date=2014-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131201080229/http://www.vancitybuzz.com/2013/07/man-of-steel-2-production-departs-vancouver-for-toronto/ |archive-date=2013-12-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

