s-deadshot-1201368867/ | archive-date=2015-06-26 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/harley-quinn-suicide-squad-movie-margot-robbie/ |title=Exclusive: Margot Robbie to Play Harley Quinn in SUICIDE SQUAD |last=Goldberg |first=Matt |date=2014-11-10 |website=Collider |publisher= |accessdate=2014-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110070459/http://collider.com/harley-quinn-suicide-squad-movie-margot-robbie/ |archive-date=2014-11-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=KillerCroc>{{cite web|url=http://comicbook.com/2015/03/31/suicide-squad-casts-adewale-akinnuoye-agbaje-as-killer-croc/|title=Suicide Squad Casts Adewale Akinnuoye-Agbaje As Killer Croc|publisher=comicbook.com|accessdate=2015-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402113804/http://comicbook.com/2015/03/31/suicide-squad-casts-adewale-akinnuoye-agbaje-as-killer-croc/|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

